.TH "ipr_alloc_ucode_buffer" 9 "ipr_alloc_ucode_buffer" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ipr_alloc_ucode_buffer \- Allocates a microcode download buffer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct ipr_sglist *" ipr_alloc_ucode_buffer
.BI "(int buf_len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "buf_len" 12
buffer length
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Allocates a DMA'able buffer in chunks and assembles a scatter/gather
list to use for microcode download

Return value:
pointer to sglist / NULL on failure
